column5: FAR from it and always the first to admit it..... count just means that I take the time to read and reply to darn near every "proud moment" that members post, as without such responses from members this board would come to a screaching halt. If all we had is takers, and no givers, OFC would be a pretty sad looking place.  I do of course get in the odd fishing outing of my own to share around here...good landscape and scenery shots anyhow!
thanks for the reply
Thanks Paul !!! That means a LOT coming from you! LOL
At this rate. I'll catch up in no time.
And to think he's only here 3/4 of the year  HH your bang on with your comments.  Wayne is a good guy! Always around to lend a hand  Geesh did I just say that out loud
lol Congrats to ya Wayne. May you make many more in good health
Dolt work gets in the way from me even coming close..  Congrats.. Imperial Angler
Congrats Wayne and to another 10,000 more!
All in good humor my FRIEND.
Maybe y'all should get a room...
well done! 10,000 is serious business.
You've passed the 10,000 post mark!!!!!!! It's 9:33, do you know where you're donkey is???  Congrats Bud. I have NO idea how many you'd be at if you didn't have a job!
PLEASE! Tell us your secret!
Wow...and I thought I had no life....LOL....  Congrats Wayne...quite the accomplishment!!!
So do I get a prize from the high up shelf, or the bottom bin in the concession stand?  Hope at least 10 of them had something of value in them.. the rest where a bunch of
And 9000 of them were pretty decent.  Congrats Wayne!!

...and to think most of those where done on dial up.  Yes Cliff... I need to get a life.  Other thing is I can type about 400 WPM.....thanks Miss Kelly...my grade 9 typing teacher that "passed me through" with 51 %. (Broke a chalk board slapping return with no tab stops set! )
Holy post count batman  Congrats loser  Hey, I'm not that far behind, I'll shut up now.  JOey
Hey...give him tickets to the Sportsman Show....LOL
Well, at least 9 out of the ten I read did,   :lol:  :lol:  Congrats Wayne.
Hey Wayne . Congrats  . Always look forward to reading your input on the board.
Maybe government will place a retroactive tax on message board posts.
Connie, for something to be taxable it has to be worth something.
I can make it worth a fifty Roy, to make this a fishing thread before the minority get restless!

You deserve the praise Wayne   . I also look forward to your posts. I can only imagine how many people you've helped ............... or at least entertained. I think you can safely assume you have earned the respect of many here. Thanks for making this site better Wayne. Along with countless other valuable contributors here, you really add to the credibility of this site.   Thanks.
10,000 eh? Guess I should read one of them some day....
WOW    but is this a good thing..............................LOL
Atta boy Wayne...congrats

WOW......just imagine how many days you've spent on this site!!!  I can't find it, but is there a feature here that will tell you that? I know some other sites I visit tell you how many hours you've been logged into the site..........it amazing how much time we waste on the puter!!!  Sinker
I'd definately have to agree with the readout on the meter!  Just kidding, you're a great resource to have on this board Wayne.  You have wisdom beyond your years...and that's a lot of years  Tony

Scary part is I spend only a couple of days from Mid-May to Late September on here!  No wonder the honey do list is growing around here....... Gotta work on that and I'll be back in a couple years to check in on OFC !  TERRY... NO it's not...and you're coming right up behind me!  Dano... Chicken coops ready for you on the 14th me lad!  Kennyman.. Thanks for the kind words... I'm not trying to "earn" any respect here, just being who I am with no "hiding" behind a keyboard. I think any that have met me / fished with me will tell you I'm the same in person as I am here. A complete    ! lol  And Tony... did you know that there are fish in Lake Temagami ?

hell, I am so far behind, they had sent out a search party.....  a year ago we were pretty close in numbers.......I slipping but they say I am getting more work done.... who da thunk it  oh and that is a nice fish..just to keep a little fishing in the thread...
Congrats to the new Imperial Angler   :worthy:  :worthy:

Congrats Wayne! I have been fortunate enough to fish with Wayne and I can tell you that yes, he is exactly the same in person as he is here on the board, the main difference being, here on the board, you can close the thread to get him to stop! LOL Keep up the good work Wayne, HH
Way to go Wayne here's to the next 10,000 !!!
wow, thats a lot of posts. You must be the best angler here.  congratulations, heres  to another 10,000 posts.
